SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';


select distinct b.ref_no, 
b.status, 
l.registration_no, 
m.name as model, 
br.name as brand, 
lp.base_price, 
to_char(b.created_at,'YYYY-MM-DD')as created_at_date,
to_char(b.created_at,'HH24:MI')as created_at_hours,
to_char(b.request_start_at,'YYYY-MM-DD')as request_start_at_date,
to_char(b.request_start_at,'HH24:MI')as request_start_at_hours,
to_char(b.request_end_at,'YYYY-MM-DD')as request_end_at_date,
to_char(b.request_end_at,'HH24:MI')as request_end_at_hours, 
 1 + DATE_PART('day', b.request_end_at - b.request_start_at) as booking_days,
concat(ll.address_line_1,' ',ll.address_line_2,' ',ll.state_region_province)as address, 
ST_X(ll.geo) AS longitude,
ST_Y(ll.geo) AS latitude
from bookings b 
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
left join listing_pricing lp on lp.listing_id = l.id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id 
left join brands br on br.id = m.brand_id 
where 1=1 
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and b.status = 'rejected'
and b.request_start_at >= NOW() + interval '6 hours'
order by 5 desc

SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.registration_no, 
lp.base_price, 
m.name as models, 
br.name as brands,
concat(ll.address_line_1,' ',ll.address_line_2,' ',ll.state_region_province)as address, 
ST_X(ll.geo) AS longitude,
ST_Y(ll.geo) AS latitude,
count(dates.ymd)as avai_days
from listings l 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
left join listing_pricing lp on lp.listing_id = l.id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id 
left join brands br on br.id = m.brand_id
left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id = l.id
left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '{{ $json.request_start_at_date }}', timestamp '{{ $json.request_end_at_date }}', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates 
on dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
where ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
and l.registration_no = '{{ $json['Car Reg Num'] }}'
group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7
